d shows BTC.D increasing as investors seek safety. Although specific current dominance data is not in the report, capital shifts to Bitcoin often occur during volatile market periods.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class="report-card">\n        <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-area"></i> In-depth Technical Analysis</h3>\n        <h4>Key BTC Price Levels:</h4>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Weak Resistance:</strong> Around $123,287</li>\n            <li><strong>Key Demand/Support Zone:</strong> $112,000 - $116,000</li>\n            <li><strong>Trend Support (Supertrend):</strong> $115,330</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h4>Momentum Indicators:</h4>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Money Flow Index (MFI):</strong> <strong style="color: var(--rsi-overbought-color);">85.27 (overbought condition)</strong>.</li>\n            <li><strong>Supertrend:</strong> Maintains bullish trend.</li>\n            <li><strong>DMI:</strong> +DI is higher than -DI, ADX is rising, signaling trend strength.</li>\n            <li><strong>Bitcoin Options Implied Volatility:</strong> At multi-year lows, often preceding major price movements.</li>\n        </ul>\n        <!-- CHART_DATA: {\n          "type": "gauge",\n          "value": 85,\n          "config": {\n            "min": 0,\n            "max": 100,\n            "segments": [\n              {"limit": 30, "color": "var(--rsi-oversold-color)", "label": "Oversold"},\n              {"limit": 70, "color": "var(--rsi-neutral-color)", "label": "Neutral"},\n              {"limit": 100, "color": "var(--rsi-overbought-color)", "label": "Overbought"}\n            ]\n          }\n        } -->\n        <div id="mfi-gauge-container-en" class="chart-container" aria-label="Money Flow Index Gauge Chart"></div>\n        <p>The MFI indicates Bitcoin is in the overbought region, requiring monitoring for potential correction. However, other trend indicators still support the upward momentum.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    